overview: In this western, a frontier detective disguised as an entertainer performs for the leader of an outlaw gang. At the same time, he learns the whereabouts of the outlaws' hideout. Unfortunately, his true identity is revealed and he must escape if he is to bring the gang to justice.
tagline: Three Sticks Of Texas Dynamite... and They Blast Border Badmen Right Out Of Their Saddles!
title: Raiders of the West
